"c13 c15 c3"><span class="c5 c1"></span></p><p class="c13 c15 c3"><span class="c5 c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 l&agrave; d&ograve;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m m&#7899;i &#273;&#7871;n t&#7915; th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u GTR, nh&#7857;m &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u n&acirc;ng c&#7845;p v&agrave; c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng nh&#432;ng kh&ocirc;ng mu&#7889;n thay &#273;&#7893;i h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;&egrave;n ch&iacute;nh. </span><span class="c1">S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 c&oacute; m&#7913;c gi&aacute; ni&ecirc;m y&#7871;t 6.000.000 VN&#272;/b&#7897; (ch&#432;a VAT) c&ugrave;ng v&#7899;i ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch b&#7843;o h&agrave;nh &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917; 2 n&#259;m t&#7841;i c&aacute;c h&#7879; th&#7889;ng GTR Vi&#7879;t Nam tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n qu&#7889;c.</span></p><table class="c20"><tr class="c2"><td class="c22" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c0"><span class="c18 c1">Tr&#7843; l&#7901;i nhanh: Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 l&agrave; m&#7851;u bi g&#7847;m LED c&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t Cos kho&#7843;ng 45W v&agrave; Pha kho&#7843;ng 75W, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh 6 Big LED k&#7871;t h&#7907;p 1+1 chip Osram tr&#7907; pha, n&#7893;i b&#7853;t v&#7899;i nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u 4800K &#273;&#7897;c b&#7843;n c&ugrave;ng c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; Pha gi&#7843; l&#7853;p Laser. Ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p cho xe th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n &#273;i m&#432;a, s&#432;&#417;ng m&ugrave; ho&#7863;c &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng. </span></p></td></tr></table><p class="c0 c10"><span class="c11 c1">T&oacute;m t&#7855;t nhanh: </span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_welbhpci53wr-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">Gi&aacute; ni&ecirc;m y&#7871;t: 6.000.000 VN&#272;/b&#7897; (ch&#432;a VAT)</span></li><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">C&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t: Cos kho&#7843;ng 45W &ndash; Pha kho&#7843;ng 75W</span></li><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">B&#7843;o h&agrave;nh &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917;: 24 th&aacute;ng</span></li><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">Ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p xe th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n &#273;i &#273;&ecirc;m, &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng, &#273;&egrave;o d&#7889;c v&agrave; s&#432;&#417;ng m&ugrave;</span></li></ul><ol class="c8 lst-kix_gbmlnd2zu5vw-0 start" start="1"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c11 c1">T&#7893;ng quan v&#7873; Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></li></ol><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c1">Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 l&agrave; d&ograve;ng &#273;&egrave;n bi g&#7847;m s&#7903; h&#7919;u hi&#7879;u su&#7845;t cao v&#7899;i l&#7889;i thi&#7871;t k&#7871; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t &#7903; c&aacute;c v&#7883; tr&iacute; th&#7845;p ph&iacute;a d&#432;&#7899;i c&#7843;n tr&#432;&#7899;c ho&#7863;c ngay t&#7841;i h&#7889;c &#273;&egrave;n g&#7847;m nguy&ecirc;n b&#7843;n c&#7911;a xe. </span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c1">&#272;i&#7875;m &#273;&aacute;ng ch&uacute; &yacute; c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m l&agrave; s&#7903; h&#7919;u c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh 6(big)+1+1 (Osram) v&#7899;i c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; gi&#7843; l&#7853;p Laser, &#273;em &#273;&#7871;n &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng m&#7841;nh m&#7869; v&#7899;i t&acirc;m s&aacute;ng v&agrave;ng &#273;&#7853;m, gom t&#7889;t v&agrave; c&oacute; chi&#7873;u s&acirc;u.</span></p><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c5 c1"></span></p><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c5 c1"></span></p><p class="c13 c15"><span class="c18 c1">&#272;&egrave;n bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c1">N&#7871;u nh&#432; &#273;&egrave;n zin c&#7911;a xe y&#7871;u, kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&#7843; n&#259;ng chi&#7871;u s&aacute;ng ho&#7863;c &#273;&#417;n thu&#7847;n mu&#7889;n n&acirc;ng c&#7845;p h&#7879; th&#7889;ng chi&#7871;u s&aacute;ng nh&#432;ng kh&ocirc;ng mu&#7889;n can thi&#7879;p &#273;&#7871;n &#273;&egrave;n chi&#7871;u s&aacute;ng ch&iacute;nh, th&igrave; Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 s&#7869; l&agrave; gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p t&#7889;i &#432;u m&agrave; ch&#7911; xe n&ecirc;n l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n. </span></p><ol class="c8 lst-kix_935s5caf96fm-0 start" start="1"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c11 c1">Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i ai?</span></li></ol><table class="c20"><tr class="c2"><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c13"><span class="c5 c1">Nhu c&#7847;u c&#7911;a ch&#7911; xe</span></p></td><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c13"><span class="c5 c1">Kh&#7843; n&#259;ng &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c2"><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c13"><span class="c5 c1">N&acirc;ng c&#7845;p &#273;&egrave;n g&#7847;m &ocirc; t&ocirc; &#273;i m&#432;a, s&#432;&#417;ng m&ugrave;, &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&egrave;o</span></p></td><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c13"><span class="c5 c1">Nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u 4800K, &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng Cos 45W m&#7841;nh m&#7869;, bao qu&aacute;t t&#7847;m nh&igrave;n 2 b&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng. </span></p></td></tr><tr class="c2"><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c13"><span class="c5 c1">H&#7895; tr&#7907; &#273;i cao t&#7889;c</span></p></td><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c13"><span class="c5 c1">C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; Pha gi&#7843; l&#7853;p Laser v&#7899;i c&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 75W v&#7899;i t&acirc;m pha h&igrave;nh elip, t&#7841;o cung s&aacute;ng c&oacute; chi&#7873;u s&acirc;u v&#7899;i t&#7847;m chi&#7871;u xa h&agrave;ng tr&#259;m m&eacute;t.</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c2"><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c13"><span class="c5 c1">Xe c&oacute; &#273;&egrave;n zin y&#7871;u nh&#432;ng kh&ocirc;ng mu&#7889;n can thi&#7879;p h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;&egrave;n ch&iacute;nh</span></p></td><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c13"><span class="c5 c1">N&acirc;ng c&#7845;p c&#7843; &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng Cos v&agrave; &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng Pha. K&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&ugrave;ng h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;&egrave;n ch&iacute;nh gi&uacute;p h&#7895; tr&#7907; c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n kh&#7843; n&#259;ng quan s&aacute;t. &nbsp; </span></p></td></tr></table><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c5 c1"></span></p><ol class="c8 lst-kix_935s5caf96fm-0" start="2"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c11 c1">&Aacute;nh s&aacute;ng th&#7921;c t&#7871; c&#7911;a Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></li></ol><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">3.1 H&#7879; th&#7889;ng &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng Cos </span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c1">&#7902; ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Cos, Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 cho ra &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng v&#7899;i c&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t m&#7841;nh m&#7869; 45W, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh 6 chip LED l&#7899;n th&#7871; h&#7879; m&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7889; tr&iacute; trong ch&oacute;a ph&#7843;n x&#7841;. &Aacute;nh s&aacute;ng Cos th&#7921;c t&#7871; cho th&#7845;y s&#7921; t&#7889;t h&#417;n so v&#7899;i d&ograve;ng &#273;&egrave;n kh&aacute;c trong c&ugrave;ng ph&acirc;n kh&uacute;c.</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_llpv8za5qwlf-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">C&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t Cos: Kho&#7843;ng 45W.</span></li><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">C&#7845;u h&igrave;nh Cos: 6 (big) chip LED</span></li><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">T&#7847;m nh&igrave;n: V&ugrave;ng s&aacute;ng r&#7897;ng t&#7915; 4 &#273;&#7871;n 5 l&agrave;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n, h&#7895; tr&#7907; ki&#7875;m so&aacute;t c&aacute;c v&#7883; tr&iacute; g&oacute;c khu&#7845;t t&#7847;m th&#7845;p. &nbsp;</span></li></ul><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c5 c1"></span></p><p class="c13 c15"><span class="c18 c1">&Aacute;nh s&aacute;ng Cos c&#7911;a bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c17 c1">3</span><span class="c11 c1">.2 H&#7879; th&#7889;ng &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng Pha gi&#7843; l&#7853;p Laser</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c1">&#7902; &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng Pha, Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 b&ugrave;ng n&#7893; s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh v&#7899;i c&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t l&ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 75W. Nh&#7901; t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p th&ecirc;m c&#7909;m 1+1 chip LED Osram cao c&#7845;p t&#7841;i c&#7909;m m&#7855;t tr&#7907; Pha, &#273;&egrave;n s&#7903; h&#7919;u c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; gi&#7843; l&#7853;p c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; Pha gi&#7843; l&#7853;p Laser theo c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh do nh&agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; cho ra &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng chi&#7871;u xa v&#7899;i kh&#7843; n&#259;ng t&#7853;p trung t&#7889;t, ngo&agrave;i ra t&acirc;m Pha Elip cho &#273;&#7897; gom t&#7841;i t&acirc;m t&#7889;t, t&#7841;o th&agrave;nh cung s&aacute;ng c&oacute; chi&#7873;u s&acirc;u. </span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_gkmfowq3kyc-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">&Aacute;nh s&aacute;ng Pha kho&#7843;ng 75W.</span></li><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">C&#7845;u h&igrave;nh Pha: 6 (big)+1+1(Osram)</span></li><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">V&ugrave;ng s&aacute;ng Pha v&#7899;i t&acirc;m Elip cho &#273;&#7897; chi&#7871;u xa cao, &#273;&#7853;m t&#7841;i t&acirc;m v&agrave; &#273;&#7897; gom t&#7889;t.</span></li></ul><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c5 c1"></span></p><p class="c13 c15"><span class="c1 c21">&Aacute;nh s&aacute;ng Pha c&#7911;a &#273;&egrave;n Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">3.3 Nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u 4800K &#273;&#7897;c b&#7843;n k&#7871;t h&#7907;p m&#7855;t tr&#7907; Pha nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u 3000K</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c1">&#272;&egrave;n s&#7903; h&#7919;u nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u t&#7893;ng th&#7875; 4800K cho ra &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng v&agrave;ng tr&#7855;ng hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, d&#7883;u m&#7855;t. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, khi &#273;&aacute; Pha, m&#7855;t tr&#7907; pha t&acirc;m 3000K s&#7869; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t, mang l&#7841;i kh&#7843; n&#259;ng xuy&ecirc;n s&#432;&#417;ng, h&#7895; tr&#7907; t&#259;ng kh&#7843; n&#259;ng b&aacute;m &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng khi &#273;i &#273;&egrave;o hay tr&#7901;i m&#432;a. &nbsp;</span></p><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c5 c1"></span></p><p class="c13 c15"><span class="c1 c18">Nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u 4800K &#273;&#7897;c b&#7843;n k&#7871;t h&#7907;p m&#7855;t tr&#7907; pha t&acirc;m 3000K.</span></p><p class="c13 c15"><span class="c18 c1">&nbsp;c&#7911;a GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></p><ol class="c8 lst-kix_935s5caf96fm-0" start="3"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c11 c1">H&#7879; th&#7889;ng t&#7843;n nhi&#7879;t &#273;&#7881;nh cao v&agrave; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng ch&#7889;ng n&#432;&#7899;c IP68</span></li></ol><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">4.1 C&#7845;u t&#7841;o nh&ocirc;m nguy&ecirc;n kh&#7889;i k&#7871;t h&#7907;p r&atilde;nh tho&aacute;t nhi&#7879;t tr&ecirc;n th&acirc;n &#273;&egrave;n</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c1">Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7871; t&#7841;o t&#7915; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u Aluminum nguy&ecirc;n kh&#7889;i cho to&agrave;n b&#7897; th&acirc;n &#273;&egrave;n v&agrave; v&#7883; tr&iacute; ch&#7909;p lens. Ngo&agrave;i ra, th&acirc;n &#273;&egrave;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c phay c&aacute;c r&atilde;nh tho&aacute;t nhi&#7879;t gi&uacute;p t&#259;ng di&#7879;n t&iacute;ch ti&#7871;p x&uacute;c v&#7899;i kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute;, gi&uacute;p t&#7889;i &#432;u t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; d&#7851;n nhi&#7879;t ra m&ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng. &nbsp;</span></p><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c5 c1"></span></p><p class="c13 c15"><span class="c18 c1">C&aacute;c r&atilde;nh tr&ecirc;n th&acirc;n &#273;&egrave;n c&#7845;u t&#7841;o t&#7915; nh&ocirc;m nguy&ecirc;n kh&#7889;i</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c17 c1">4</span><span class="c11 c1">.2 Qu&#7841;t t&#7843;n nhi&#7879;t ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng d&#432;&#7899;i th&acirc;n (&#273;u&ocirc;i) &#273;&egrave;n</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c1">Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 trang b&#7883; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng qu&#7841;t l&agrave;m m&aacute;t ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7889; tr&iacute; d&#432;&#7899;i th&acirc;n (&#273;u&ocirc;i) &#273;&egrave;n, v&#7853;n h&agrave;nh li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c &#273;&#7875; c&#432;&#7905;ng b&#7913;c lu&#7891;ng kh&iacute; n&oacute;ng tho&aacute;t ra ngo&agrave;i, duy tr&igrave; nhi&#7879;t &#273;&#7897; c&#7911;a chip LED &#7903; ng&#432;&#7905;ng an to&agrave;n, ng&#259;n ng&#7915;a t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng suy gi&#7843;m c&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t khi &#273;&egrave;n ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c trong th&#7901;i gian d&agrave;i. &nbsp;</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c1">Ngo&agrave;i ra, &#273;&egrave;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p l&#7895; th&ocirc;ng h&#417;i ch&#7889;ng h&#7845;p h&#417;i n&#432;&#7899;c, h&#7895; tr&#7907; c&acirc;n b&#7857;ng &aacute;p su&#7845;t v&agrave; &#273;&#7897; &#7849;m b&ecirc;n trong v&agrave; b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i, ng&#259;n ng&#7915;a hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&#7885;ng s&#432;&#417;ng tr&ecirc;n m&#7863;t k&iacute;nh khi c&oacute; s&#7921; ch&ecirc;nh l&#7879;ch nhi&#7879;t &#273;&#7897; &#273;&#7897;t ng&#7897;t. </span></p><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c5 c1"></span></p><p class="c13 c15"><span class="c18 c1">Qu&#7841;t t&#7843;n nhi&#7879;t ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng d&#432;&#7899;i th&acirc;n (&#273;u&ocirc;i) &#273;&egrave;n v&agrave; n&uacute;t th&ocirc;ng h&#417;i</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">4.3 Ch&#7889;ng n&#432;&#7899;c, ch&#7889;ng b&#7909;i IP68</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c1">Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo &#273;&#7841;t ch&#7881; IP68, &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o kh&#7843; n&#259;ng kh&aacute;ng b&#7909;i ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n v&agrave; ch&#7889;ng x&acirc;m nh&#7853;p c&#7911;a n&#432;&#7899;c khi xe di chuy&#7875;n qua c&aacute;c v&ugrave;ng ng&#7853;p n&#432;&#7899;c, v&#7853;n h&agrave;nh d&#432;&#7899;i tr&#7901;i m&#432;a ho&#7863;c khi r&#7917;a xe. </span></p><ol class="c8 lst-kix_935s5caf96fm-0" start="4"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c11 c1">Th&ocirc;ng s&#7889; n&#7893;i b&#7853;t c&#7911;a &#273;&egrave;n Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></li></ol><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c11 c1"></span></p><table class="c20"><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">Th&ocirc;ng s&#7889; k&#7929; thu&#7853;t</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">Chi ti&#7871;t c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">T&ecirc;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">K&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c Lens</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">3.0 inch</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">V&#7883; tr&iacute; l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">&#272;&egrave;n g&#7847;m/ S&#432;&#417;ng m&ugrave;</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">K&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c &#272;&egrave;n</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">129x67x80 mm</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">C&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t Cos (Low Beam)</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">~45W</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c23"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">C&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t Pha (High Beam)</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">~75W</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">Nh&acirc;n LED</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">6 (big)</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">M&#7855;t tr&#7907; Pha</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">1+1 (Osram) </span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; n&#7893;i b&#7853;t</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">Nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u 4800K &#273;&#7897;c b&#7843;n - Pha gi&#7843; l&#7853;p Laser</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c23"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">Nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">4800K</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">&#272;i&#7879;n &aacute;p ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">12V - 16V</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">Ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n ch&#7889;ng n&#432;&#7899;c</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">IP68</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">Tu&#7893;i th&#7885; trung b&igrave;nh</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">30.000 Gi&#7901; (Theo c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; nh&agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t)</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">Ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">Aluminum nguy&ecirc;n kh&#7889;i</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c16"><td class="c4" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">Ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; b&#7843;o h&agrave;nh</span></p></td><td class="c9" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c12"><span class="c5 c1">24 th&aacute;ng</span></p></td></tr></table><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c11 c1"></span></p><ol class="c8 lst-kix_935s5caf96fm-0" start="5"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c11 c1">Quy tr&igrave;nh l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t c&#7911;a Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></li></ol><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c11 c1"></span></p><table class="c20"><tr class="c2"><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c13"><span class="c11 c1">B&#432;&#7899;c</span></p></td><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c13"><span class="c11 c1">N&#7897;i dung th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c2"><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><ol class="c8 lst-kix_at2ladsq84ti-0 start" start="1"><li class="c14 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">Ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n v&agrave; ki&#7875;m tra xe</span></li></ol></td><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c14"><span class="c5 c1">Ki&#7875;m tra t&#7893;ng th&#7875; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;i&#7879;n, &#273;&egrave;n g&#7847;m nguy&ecirc;n b&#7843;n v&agrave; t&#432; v&#7845;n ph&#432;&#417;ng &aacute;n ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p cho t&#7915;ng d&ograve;ng xe.</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c2"><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><ol class="c8 lst-kix_at2ladsq84ti-0" start="2"><li class="c14 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">L&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></li></ol></td><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c14"><span class="c5 c1">L&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t b&#7857;ng p&aacute;t chuy&ecirc;n d&#7909;ng, &#273;i d&acirc;y, c&#7889; &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&egrave;n.</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c2"><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><ol class="c8 lst-kix_at2ladsq84ti-0" start="3"><li class="c14 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">C&#259;n ch&#7881;nh t&acirc;m s&aacute;ng v&agrave; &#273;&#7897; cao</span></li></ol></td><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c14"><span class="c5 c1">Ki&#7875;m tra ti&ecirc;u c&#7921;, &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh &#273;&#7897; cao &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng c&#7855;t s&aacute;ng v&agrave; &#273;&#7897; ph&#7911; quang th&ocirc;ng &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n k&#7929; thu&#7853;t. &nbsp;</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c2"><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><ol class="c8 lst-kix_at2ladsq84ti-0" start="4"><li class="c6 c14 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">Ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n v&agrave; b&agrave;n giao</span></li></ol></td><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c14"><span class="c5 c1">H&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng, ki&#7875;m tra l&#7841;i &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng th&#7921;c t&#7871; sau khi l&#7855;p.</span></p></td></tr><tr class="c2"><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><ol class="c8 lst-kix_at2ladsq84ti-0" start="5"><li class="c14 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">K&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t b&#7843;o h&agrave;nh &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917;</span></li></ol></td><td class="c7" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="c14"><span class="c5 c1">H&#7895; tr&#7907; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tra c&#7913;u v&agrave; l&#432;u th&ocirc;ng tin b&#7843;o h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng.</span></p></td></tr></table><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c5 c1"></span></p><ol class="c8 lst-kix_935s5caf96fm-0" start="6"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c11 c1">&#272;&#7883;a ch&#7881; l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t &#273;&egrave;n Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2</span></li></ol><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c1">T&#7841;i h&#7879; th&#7889;ng Auto365, kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7897;i ng&#361; k&#7929; thu&#7853;t vi&ecirc;n t&#432; v&#7845;n v&#7873; nhu c&#7847;u l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t &#273;&egrave;n c&#361;ng nh&#432; qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh thi c&ocirc;ng l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t, c&#259;n ch&#7881;nh g&oacute;c chi&#7871;u &#273;&uacute;ng k&#7929; thu&#7853;t. </span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_upu3atfwp4pp-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">T&#432; v&#7845;n ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i nhu c&#7847;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng.</span></li><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">Thi c&ocirc;ng &#273;&uacute;ng k&#7929; thu&#7853;t v&agrave; quy tr&igrave;nh l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t &#273;&egrave;n, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng p&aacute;t chuy&ecirc;n d&#7909;ng, &#273;i d&acirc;y, c&#7889; &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&egrave;n v&agrave; ki&#7875;m tra &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c khi b&agrave;n giao. </span></li><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">H&#7879; th&#7889;ng to&agrave;n qu&#7889;c: L&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t t&#7841;i c&aacute;c c&#417; s&#7903; thu&#7897;c Auto365, GTR Vi&#7879;t Nam v&agrave; X-Light Vi&#7879;t Nam. </span></li><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c1">B&#7843;o h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng: GTR G1 Turbo &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7843;o h&agrave;nh 2 n&#259;m, kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; ki&#7875;m tra b&#7857;ng seri sau khi k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng. </span><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"></li></ul><p class="c0 c10"><span class="c11 c1">T&#7892;NG H&#7906;P C&Acirc;U H&#7886;I FAQ V&#7872; GTR G1 TURBO V2</span></p><p class="c0 c3 c10"><span class="c11 c1"></span></p><p class="c0 c3"><span class="c1 c11"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 1: Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 c&oacute; gi&aacute; bao nhi&ecirc;u?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_4plijdyxuknj-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">Gi&aacute; ni&ecirc;m y&#7871;t c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m l&agrave; 6.000.000 VN&#272;/b&#7897; (ch&#432;a bao g&#7891;m VAT). T&#7893;ng chi ph&iacute; ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n c&oacute; th&#7875; dao &#273;&#7897;ng t&ugrave;y thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o c&#7845;u tr&uacute;c c&#7911;a t&#7915;ng d&ograve;ng xe (ph&aacute;t sinh th&ecirc;m p&aacute;t chuy&ecirc;n d&#7909;ng, gi&#7855;c chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i ngu&#7891;n ho&#7863;c can thi&#7879;p k&#7929; thu&#7853;t h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;i&#7879;n). </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 2: Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 b&#7843;o h&agrave;nh m&#7845;y n&#259;m?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_qalyqzubyu23-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7843;o h&agrave;nh &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917; ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng trong th&#7901;i gian 24 th&aacute;ng t&#7841;i c&aacute;c trung t&acirc;m thu&#7897;c h&#7879; th&#7889;ng GTR Vi&#7879;t Nam tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n qu&#7889;c d&#7921;a theo s&#7889; seri c&#7911;a &#273;&egrave;n. &nbsp;</span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 3: Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 c&oacute; m&#7845;y phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_by3jxr8y2uqi-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&#7881; c&oacute; duy nh&#7845;t m&#7897;t phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh: Nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u t&#7893;ng th&#7875; 4800K (ti&#7879;m c&#7853;n v&ugrave;ng &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng trung t&iacute;nh) ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p c&ugrave;ng m&#7855;t tr&#7907; pha t&acirc;m 3000K. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 4: Tu&#7893;i th&#7885; c&#7911;a &#273;&egrave;n bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c bao nhi&ecirc;u n&#259;m?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_pcm1az6sp8tu-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c1 c17">L&ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 30.000 gi&#7901; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng</span><span class="c5 c1">&nbsp;theo th&ocirc;ng s&#7889; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; t&#7915; nh&agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t. &#272;&#7897; b&#7873;n th&#7921;c t&#7871; t&ugrave;y thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o t&#7847;n su&#7845;t v&#7853;n h&agrave;nh. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 5: C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; n&#7893;i b&#7853;t c&#7911;a Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 l&agrave; g&igrave;?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_rqngv5hkb6ck-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; n&#7893;i b&#7853;t c&#7911;a Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 l&agrave; nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u 4800K &#273;&#7897;c b&#7843;n v&agrave; t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng Pha gi&#7843; l&#7853;p Laser, gi&uacute;p t&#7889;i &#432;u h&oacute;a kh&#7843; n&#259;ng ph&acirc;n b&#7893; lu&#7891;ng s&aacute;ng. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 6: Th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n di chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&egrave;o, s&#432;&#417;ng m&ugrave; c&oacute; n&ecirc;n l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t &#273;&egrave;n bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 kh&ocirc;ng?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_gl7u2h6htp8s-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c17 c1">C&oacute;, r&#7845;t ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p.</span><span class="c5 c1">&nbsp;Khi b&#7853;t Pha, m&#7855;t tr&#7907; pha 3000K (&aacute;nh s&aacute;ng v&agrave;ng) ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i gi&uacute;p t&#259;ng kh&#7843; n&#259;ng b&aacute;m &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng, xuy&ecirc;n s&#432;&#417;ng m&#432;a. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 7: Nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u c&#7911;a m&#7855;t tr&#7907; Pha &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;o?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_8ta42egs7jdc-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c1">M&#7855;t tr&#7907; pha &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh &#273;&#7897;c l&#7853;p v&#7899;i nhi&#7879;t m&agrave;u 3000K, t&#7853;p trung lu&#7891;ng s&aacute;ng t&#7841;i v&ugrave;ng trung t&acirc;m c&#7911;a ch&ugrave;m Pha. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 8: C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &lsquo;gi&#7843; l&#7853;p Laser&rsquo; tr&ecirc;n GTR G1 Turbo V2 ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;o?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_gg2yzlwcpedp-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">S&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&#7909;m 1+1 chip LED Osram t&#7841;o t&acirc;m pha Elip gom cao. Th&ocirc;ng s&#7889; chi&#7871;u xa 1000m ghi nh&#7853;n theo c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; c&#7911;a nh&agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n th&#7917; nghi&#7879;m l&yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng, th&#7921;c t&#7871; thay &#273;&#7893;i theo m&ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 9: C&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t ti&ecirc;u th&#7909; th&#7921;c t&#7871; c&#7911;a &#273;&egrave;n l&agrave; bao nhi&ecirc;u? </span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_ph2e4k34y5im-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">&#7902; ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Cos (Low Beam), c&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t ti&ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#7841;t kho&#7843;ng 45W. &#7902; ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; Pha (High Beam), t&#7893;ng c&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t ti&ecirc;u th&#7909; c&#7911;a h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;&#7841;t kho&#7843;ng 75W. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 10: &#272;&#7897; m&#7903; r&#7897;ng v&ugrave;ng s&aacute;ng (&#273;&#7897; r&#7897;ng ch&ugrave;m Cos) &#273;&#7841;t ph&#7841;m vi bao nhi&ecirc;u? </span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_ql8tqdkvv71d-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">&#7902; c&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t Cos 45W, g&oacute;c m&#7903; c&#7911;a th&#7845;u k&iacute;nh cho ph&eacute;p &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng bao ph&#7911; chi&#7873;u ngang t&#7915; 4 &#273;&#7871;n 5 l&agrave;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 11: T&#7847;m chi&#7871;u xa bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 c&oacute; g&igrave; n&#7893;i b&#7853;t?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_rcd9v91ueaju-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">&#272;&#7841;t &#273;&#7871;n 1000m theo c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; c&#7911;a nh&agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n th&#7917; nghi&#7879;m l&yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng nh&#7901; c&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t Pha ~75W. &nbsp;</span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 12: T&acirc;m Pha h&igrave;nh Elip c&oacute; vai tr&ograve; g&igrave; trong ph&acirc;n b&#7893; &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng? &nbsp;</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_xcbde6ajnx99-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c17 c1">Tr&#7843; l&#7901;i:</span><span class="c1">&nbsp;T&acirc;m Pha Elip c&oacute; vai tr&ograve; t&#7853;p trung c&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7897; s&aacute;ng cao nh&#7845;t v&agrave;o khu v&#7921;c trung t&acirc;m c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i l&aacute;i, h&#7841;n ch&#7871; t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng b&#7883; ph&acirc;n t&aacute;n l&ecirc;n cao ho&#7863;c sang hai b&ecirc;n, t&#7915; &#273;&oacute; h&#7895; tr&#7907; c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n t&#7847;m nh&igrave;n xa t&#7889;t h&#417;n. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 13: V&#7883; tr&iacute; l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t chu&#7849;n x&aacute;c c&#7911;a thi&#7871;t b&#7883; tr&ecirc;n xe &#7903; &#273;&acirc;u? </span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_1g51py4582gm-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">&#272;&egrave;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; &#273;&#7875; l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t t&#7841;i v&#7883; tr&iacute; &#273;&egrave;n g&#7847;m d&#432;&#7899;i c&#7843;n tr&#432;&#7899;c ho&#7863;c thay th&#7871; tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p v&agrave;o v&#7883; tr&iacute; h&#7889;c &#273;&egrave;n s&#432;&#417;ng m&ugrave; nguy&ecirc;n b&#7843;n c&#7911;a ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 14: &#272;&egrave;n c&oacute; v&agrave;o n&#432;&#7899;c khi &#273;i m&#432;a ho&#7863;c r&#7917;a xe kh&ocirc;ng? </span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_bewczdys2x02-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">&#272;&egrave;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7855;p r&aacute;p k&iacute;n theo ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n IP68, ng&#259;n ch&#7863;n s&#7921; x&acirc;m nh&#7853;p c&#7911;a b&#7909;i v&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c d&#432;&#7899;i &aacute;p l&#7921;c ch&#7845;t l&#7887;ng th&ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 15: &#272;&egrave;n bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 c&oacute; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i c&aacute;c d&ograve;ng xe &#273;i&#7879;n kh&ocirc;ng?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_au39mzghrywp-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">Kh&#7843; n&#259;ng t&#432;&#417;ng th&iacute;ch ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;i&#7879;n c&#7911;a t&#7915;ng d&ograve;ng xe. Ch&#7911; xe c&#7847;n k&#7929; thu&#7853;t vi&ecirc;n chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p ki&#7875;m tra t&iacute;nh t&#432;&#417;ng th&iacute;ch tr&#432;&#7899;c khi &#273;&#7845;u n&#7889;i. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 16: &#272;&egrave;n c&oacute; hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng h&#7845;p h&#417;i n&#432;&#7899;c v&agrave;o m&#7863;t k&iacute;nh khi &#273;i tr&#7901;i m&#432;a ho&#7863;c sau khi r&#7917;a xe kh&ocirc;ng?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_2ysgbbmaxn9n-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">&#272;&#432;&#7907;c h&#7841;n ch&#7871; t&#7889;i &#273;a nh&#7901; t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p c&aacute;c n&uacute;t th&ocirc;ng h&#417;i th&#7871; h&#7879; m&#7899;i gi&uacute;p c&acirc;n b&#7857;ng &aacute;p su&#7845;t v&agrave; &#273;&#7897; &#7849;m b&ecirc;n trong th&#7845;u k&iacute;nh. &nbsp;</span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 17: C&ocirc;ng su&#7845;t Pha kho&#7843;ng 75W th&igrave; &#273;&egrave;n c&oacute; b&#7883; qu&aacute; nhi&#7879;t hay nhanh h&#7887;ng kh&ocirc;ng?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_3infhwxt76d4-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">Kh&ocirc;ng. Tu&#7893;i th&#7885; linh ki&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o nh&#7901; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng gi&#7843;i nhi&#7879;t &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897;: k&#7871;t h&#7907;p gi&#7919;a t&#7843;n nhi&#7879;t th&#7909; &#273;&#7897;ng Aluminum phay r&atilde;nh v&agrave; qu&#7841;t t&#7843;n nhi&#7879;t ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng d&#432;&#7899;i th&acirc;n (&#273;u&ocirc;i) &#273;&egrave;n gi&uacute;p gi&#7843;i ph&oacute;ng nhi&#7879;t l&#432;&#7907;ng li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c, gi&#7919; chip LED ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng trong gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n nhi&#7879;t &#273;&#7897; cho ph&eacute;p.</span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 18: C&oacute; n&ecirc;n &#273;&#7897; bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 &#273;&#7875; ch&#7841;y xe d&#7883;ch v&#7909;, xe du l&#7883;ch kh&ocirc;ng?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_syj7sa5ro9b0-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">&nbsp;Ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p. Do &#273;&#7863;c th&ugrave; c&oacute; v&ugrave;ng s&aacute;ng Cos r&#7897;ng v&agrave; t&acirc;m Pha b&aacute;m &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; h&#7895; tr&#7907; t&#7889;i &#432;u t&#7847;m nh&igrave;n t&#7847;m th&#7845;p ban &#273;&ecirc;m, gi&#7843;m t&#7843;i &aacute;p l&#7921;c &#273;i&#7873;u ti&#7871;t m&#7855;t cho ng&#432;&#7901;i l&aacute;i tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c cung &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&agrave;i. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 19: L&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 c&oacute; &#273;&#259;ng ki&#7875;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave; g&acirc;y ch&oacute;i xe &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n kh&ocirc;ng?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_gw8fhgo4u6tl-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c5 c1">&#272;&#432;&#7901;ng c&#7855;t s&aacute;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#259;n ch&#7881;nh &#273;&uacute;ng k&#7929; thu&#7853;t c&oacute; th&#7875; h&#7895; tr&#7907; h&#7841;n ch&#7871; t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng ch&oacute;i m&#7855;t cho ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n. V&#7873; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; ph&aacute;p l&yacute;, vi&#7879;c &#273;&#259;ng ki&#7875;m ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng th&#7921;c t&#7871; c&#7911;a xe, quy &#273;&#7883;nh ph&aacute;p l&yacute; &aacute;p d&#7909;ng t&#7841;i th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m ki&#7875;m &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#259;n ch&#7881;nh ti&ecirc;u c&#7921;, &#273;&#7897; cao th&#7921;c t&#7871; khi thi c&ocirc;ng.. </span></li></ul><p class="c0"><span class="c11 c1">C&acirc;u h&#7887;i 20: L&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t Bi g&#7847;m GTR G1 Turbo V2 ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng &#7903; &#273;&acirc;u?</span></p><ul class="c8 lst-kix_wmxts0z91e66-0 start"><li class="c0 c6 li-bullet-0"><span class="c1 c5">Vi&#7879;c l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t n&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i c&aacute;c trung t&acirc;m &#7911;y quy&#7873;n ho&#7863;c &#273;&#7841;i l&yacute; ch&iacute;nh th&#7913;c thu&#7897;c h&#7879; th&#7889;ng Auto365, GTR Vi&#7879;t Nam v&agrave; X-Light Vi&#7879;t Nam &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o p&aacute;t chuy&ecirc;n d&#7909;ng ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p, h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;i&#7879;n &#273;&#7845;u n&#7889;i an to&agrave;n v&agrave; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t h&#7879; th&#7889;ng b&#7843;o h&agrave;nh &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917; to&agrave;n qu&#7889;c. </span></li></ul><p class="c0 c3"><span c